    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "It's as if the darkness is the only thing that feels honest anymore. Everyone else is so full of pretend and false hope... it feels so exhausting to fight it. Do you really think that the stillness is better? That it would be more beautiful to just... let go than to keep lying to myself?",
