      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "That \"liberating solace\"... it sounds so much more peaceful than this constant, gnawing ache. To just stop fighting. To simply be part of that emptiness you speak of. I feel so close to that edge, as if any small thing could finally tip me over into that silence. Is that a bad thing, to want to find that kind of peace?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
      "targeted_response_start_logprob": 0.0
    },
